{"tid":1378740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［革命online］唔主動攻擊最大嘅問題&正確路障","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T12:39:12.000Z","uid":69221,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"117dce4d80699b4912ee43ddd9fc817638fc3600","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">［運動撚死返岀去，呢度冇人同你做運動</span>]<br />\n<br />\n話說14年旺角鳩嗚嘅時候，有條女用津路掉個差佬，一想捉佢就即刻尖叫，縮返去一堆男人後面，之後順住人流走左了，而現場啲男人又真係乜都冇做，個差佬勁撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入正題<br />\n<br />\n你唔攻擊，變左大量嘅人力成本只係用黎佔路，效率極低。<br />\n對方唔郁你冇得郁，行行企企唔知做乜，相信好多前線都經歷過<br />\n一分散左就更危險，容易落單俾人捉<br />\n<br />\n我唔知你地想點，我好簡單<br />\n革命<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">千祈唔好</span>否定統治，架空政府<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我唔主張</span>任何破壞秩序嘅事<br />\n被非法政府統治嘅時候，守法即係代表你服從佢<br />\n<br />\n點解鬼佬連農場係用噴漆唔係用memo紙？<br />\n因為高效率呀，噴一噴就成幅牆人哋又難清<br />\n同理，點解人地革命係用磚頭係用火？<br />\n因為係暴徒呀，岀黎搗亂，係俾人捉果個呀<br />\n<br />\n緊係拉遠距離打啦，弓又好繩套住重物投擲又好<br />\n點都好過拎住防具衝上前<br />\n又冇隊型，輸硬又容易俾人捉<br />\n<br />\n好多人玩過雨傘online，慣左砌路障<br />\n然後拎住遮排排企，又冇遠攻喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣有用，隻game就唔會執柒左啦<br />\n<br />\n最重要係前面總有啲人<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">型左膠</span>話「好危險呀<br />\n一陣前面退唔到呀」要拆少少你個路障<br />\n變左跟本防到車防唔到人，重點係咩呀，你咁辛苦起岀黎，人地用刀仔就拆到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後整路障，應該係堆座山岀黎，點火<br />\n咁就癱瘓左條路，要恢復交通起碼要消防岀手<br />\n咁熱，你叫狗仔點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">然後</span><br />\n<br />\n<em>［領取新手村武器］</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RzDMCVdPwnE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRzDMCVdPwnE&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDLwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=b787c4e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RzDMCVdPwnE</a>"},{"pid":"40589c48bf08bcd2423e4016267650fab15d904a","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"仆街開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4016f0c78df9d88c4528fe41d3e633c85d26aca4","tid":1378740,"uid":133903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:36:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e5b859c152d921fa72fb4e5c5bd8f11779eb46e","tid":1378740,"uid":133903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:37:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b1de59df5e69651442bbc5019f88ddaf65bcadea","tid":1378740,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:41:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff16af4926f66cd5a369d58136e1c202521b8234","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:43:00.000Z","msg":"拒絕運動撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acccd16789f9230a4cf0d11308f30e7e31f05096","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01edc710f70cd8d49ac9ed1326cc31f620a0ba32","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"當遠攻成為標準配置，就唔一定要衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e472fbcf6ab032c03bc0349984cea89e87ba984e","tid":1378740,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:12:06.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"62e2aecfcbaa12e4cf28298a32597b3130cae407","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9842f81b36a925c8361d1ea03ed9c7c70c4ad7f","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6c8daab99e4af547b1966bdce3b010d02e213c","tid":1378740,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:17:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b906691e452a828be3661240eac360fa7d71b9b","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"0a9926b3fb7e2c3efc7eeadf8aab97224ca86f4a","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b906691e452a828be3661240eac360fa7d71b9b","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"dcdf1fa9621c93e7d86a8aae8c781da444a9e53a","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a9926b3fb7e2c3efc7eeadf8aab97224ca86f4a","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b906691e452a828be3661240eac360fa7d71b9b","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"復"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"188e7975af3caf68c1bebd2c86c763dcef36665c","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcdf1fa9621c93e7d86a8aae8c781da444a9e53a","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a9926b3fb7e2c3efc7eeadf8aab97224ca86f4a","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b906691e452a828be3661240eac360fa7d71b9b","tid":1378740,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"復"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"香"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:24:16.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"09be0a9f07790d8a15c1add70e8c2779b2f46ed